                  <summary source="#WinternitzKeith1905">The Liṅgānuśāsanavivaraṇoddhāra, a commentary on his own Liṅgānusāsana, by Hemacandra</summary>
                  <textLang mainLang="sa">Sanskrit.</textLang>
                  <msItem> 
                     
                     
                  <incipit source="#WinternitzKeith1905">namaḥ śrīsarvajñāya ǁ śrīsiddhahemacaṃdra | vyākaraṇaniveśitāni liṃgāni | ācāryahemacaṃdro | vivṛṇoty arhaṃ namaskṛtya ǁ 1 ǁ pulliṃgaṃ kaṭaṇa-thapabhamayaraṣasasnvaṃ | tamimanalaukistiv | nanaḍau ghaghaḍau daḥ ki | rbhāve khokarttari ca kaḥ syāt ǁ 1 ǁ It ka ṭa ṇa tha pa bha ma ya ra ṣa sa s u n | aṃtaṃ | imana | al | kistiv | na naḍ | gha | ghaḍ ǁ kādir varṇāṃ ma aṃtāṃtaṃ | imādipratyayāṃtaṃ ca | nāma | pulliṃgaṃ syāt | &amp;c.</incipit><explicit source="#WinternitzKeith1905">smṛtā kapaṭiśṛṃgyāṃ ca mahāghoṣā manīṣibhiḥ ǁ ityādi ǁ 4 ǁ niḥśeṣanāmaliṃgānuśāsanāny abhisaṃkṣepāt | ācāryahemacaṃdraḥ samadṛbhadanuśāsanāni liṃgāni ǁ 5 ǁ śrī ǁ ity ācāryaśrīhemacaṃdraviracitaisvopajñaliṃgānu-śāsanavivaraṇoddhāraḥ ǁ śrī ǁ iti Liṃgānuśāsanasūtravṛtti samāptā |</explicit></msItem>
